Stand right here.

282
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,840
Who let you be the Chief Papermaker?

283
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,160
Did you get my permission?

284
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:29,800
And you just took the mould.

285
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,800
I was just trying it for fun.

286
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,600
Making paper isn't a game.

287
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:35,240
And it can't be played with.

288
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,320
You stand right here for me.

289
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,000
Stand for one hour.

290
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,000
Reflect on what you've done.

291
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,080
What are you so smug about?

292
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,320
Chief and assistant papermaker, back in the day,

293
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,840
they were all called paper beggars.

294
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,320
What did you say?

295
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:48,640
Say that again.

296
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,400
In your eyes,

297
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,880
we're all just paper beggars?

298
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,320
Little Stone.

299
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,000
You're still so young.

300
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,560
Why do you degrade yourself like this?

301
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,720
With your attitude toward papermaking,

302
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,560
how could you ever make good paper?

303
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:03,960
How will you live your life?

304
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,440
How will you stand in this world?

305
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,960
Director Xuan.

306
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:14,000
All day it's standing punishments or reciting ancestral teachings.

307
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:16,040
Treating yourself like a feudal Shed Master.

308
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,080
You want to be the Shed Master of a paper shed?

309
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,640
This is a state-owned factory.

310
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,560
It's not one of those old paper sheds.

311
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,640
And there's no Shed Master here.

312
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:30,960
Little Stone already has gray hair.

313
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:32,440
Shi Quan, just like you back then,

314
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,800
is now a production director too.

315
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,920
Director Shi now.

316
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:37,920
Master.

317
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,560
For 28 years, I've always wanted to say...

318
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:48,640
Master.

319
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:50,680
I was wrong.

320
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,200
I was wrong.

321
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:56,320
It's been such a long time now.

322
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:58,600
There's no right or wrong anymore.

323
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:01,560
Little Stone.

324
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:03,960
Go fetch me some Wu Spring Water.

325
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,120
Master, you...

326
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,240
I want to take a sip.

327
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,240
Go on, hurry.

328
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,080
Hello, everyone.

329
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,800
Good, good, hello Director Xuan.

330
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:13,800
I'm so happy to see the masters of our factory.

331
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:16,360
I haven't seen Uncle Xuan this happy in a long time.

332
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:20,240
Right, because we're all Xuan paper artisans.

333
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,360
This is good water.

334
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:37,240
Only water this good

335
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:39,840
can make good paper.

336
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,800
Wonderful, wonderful.

337
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,200
To be honest,

338
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,600
before Master Xuan arrived,

339
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:52,240
deep down, I wasn't sure

340
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,320
we could pull this off.

341
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:55,600
After all,

342
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,560
what we're doing this time

343
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,320
is to break new ground

344
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:04,319
in the thousand-year history of Xuan paper.

345
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,359
But you know,

346
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:09,599
when I saw Master Xuan's spirit today,

347
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:13,280
my heart lit right up.

348
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,440
No more need for words.

349
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,280
Master Xuan,

350
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:19,599
it's settled then.

351
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:22,560
The Three-Zhang-Three large Xuan paper,

352
00:17:23,119 --> 00:17:24,440
we're not just going to make it,

353
00:17:25,839 --> 00:17:28,319
we'll make it, and make it well.

354
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:32,040
Master Xuan's partnership with our Hongxing Factory

355
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,360
can only succeed.

356
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,640
Failure is not an option.

357
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:41,560
Now our project's leadership team

358
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,960
is fully assembled and ready.

359
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:44,920
Master Xuan,

360
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:47,640
you and Master Lao Man

361
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:51,200
will jointly serve as Chief Engineers of this project.

362
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,000
How's that?

363
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,800
Deputy Manager Jiang Chen,

364
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:59,640
you'll handle the execution details.

365
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,480
All right.

366
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:00,600
Good.

367
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:02,360
My job is,

368
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:05,360
from everyone's daily needs

369
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:07,240
to the workshops,

370
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:09,240
the raw materials,

371
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:11,320
the technical support, and so on,

372
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,920
in every aspect,

373
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:16,560
to mobilize every resource we can

374
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,200
and fully support

375
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:20,680
the smooth progress of our project.

376
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:22,000
And to provide everyone

377
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:24,400
with the best service in everything.

378
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,680
Are you all satisfied?

379
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,080
Great!

380
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,400
Master Xuan,

381
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,200
everyone,

382
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:39,240
twenty-eight years ago,

383
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:43,200
the factory appointed Master Xuan

384
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:47,680
as Hongxing Factory's Chief Engineer.

385
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:51,800
This appointment letter was signed back then.

386
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:54,880
But in a fit of anger, you resigned.

387
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,480
Look at that, what a shame.

388
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:58,520
And so,

389
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,680
this appointment letter

390
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:05,800
sat in the archives for twenty-eight years.

391
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:07,320
Now,

392
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:10,120
I formally announce,

393
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:12,400
on behalf of Hongxing Factory,

394
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,920
that this long-overdue,

395
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,200
twenty-eight-year-old appointment letter

396
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:21,920
is officially presented to Master Xuan Yongnian.

397
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,720
Keep it as a memento.

398
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:25,480
Thank you, thank you, Chairman Guan.

399
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:26,200
Let's give him a round of applause.

400
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:28,400
Good, good.

401
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:41,280
This Hongxing Factory, normally,

402
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:43,400
keeps a pretty low profile.

403
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:46,520
But when something big comes up,

404
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:49,920
that boldness of theirs really shows.

405
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:53,840
This time they set up six teams.

406
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,800
Just the sheet-forming section alone,

407
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:58,480
they split it into two teams.

408
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:01,520
A paper vat team and a mould frame team.

409
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:04,680
And there's a mechanical team too.

410
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,440
A mould frame this huge,

411
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:09,200
they have to raise it with pulley machinery.

412
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:11,560
So they set up mechanical rails too.

413
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,080
And there's one more thing,

414
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,280
I bet none of you have ever seen it.

415
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:17,720
I sure never have.

416
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:19,720
The workshop.

417
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,720
It's enormous.

418
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,440
Never mind Three-Zhang-Three,

419
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,360
even Four-Zhang-Two Xuan paper,

420
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:27,080
they could make it, no problem.

421
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:29,800
And there's more.

422
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,840
There's also a labor team.

423
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:34,120
They set it all up exactly as I asked.

424
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:36,560
Out of over 300 sheet-forming workers,

425
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:38,520
they picked 43 people.

426
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:41,400
And every one of them's a master.

427
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,520
And the most crucial part?

428
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:45,280
Their Chief Papermaker captain,

429
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,480
they want me to pick him myself.

430
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,680
To make the final call myself.

431
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:51,880
Now that's impressive.

432
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:54,680
On top of that, Hongxing Factory

433
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:58,480
even has a dedicated technical team.

434
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,520
And what does that technical team handle?

435
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:03,000
Like what materials to use.

436
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,440
Wood, or steel,

437
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,680
or aluminum alloy.

438
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:10,000
Weight, tensile strength, all that data.

439
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:12,440
They calculate it all crystal clear.

440
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:14,080
Here, Dad, have some water.

441
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:15,560
There's a material selection team too.

442
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,280
Just the material selection team alone,

443
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:19,040
they assigned me four people for it.

444
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:23,920
All the processed bark and straw,

445
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,840
we pick only the very best.

446
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,720
They want me to select it myself.

447
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:29,200
To decide it myself.

448
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:30,320
Yongnian,

449
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:31,960
the way you're hyping it all up,

450
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:33,200
somehow I feel like

451
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:35,520
you're commanding a mighty army.

452
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,520
I'm not exaggerating.

453
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:43,360
At my age,

454
00:21:43,360 --> 00:21:44,440
why would I make a fuss?

455
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:44,800
Exactly.

456
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:46,920
Let's be honest here.

457
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:49,640
Hongxing Factory really is impressive.

458
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,440
Well-organized and powerful.

459
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:54,480
Back when my dad was at our factory,

460
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,320
how many people could he manage?

461
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:58,000
Now Hongxing has so many people,

462
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,240
it's honestly hard to keep up.

463
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:01,960
Yongnian,

464
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:05,720
have you decided the mould frame material?

465
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:07,040
Fir wood.

466
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,360
For one, it's lightweight.

467
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,360
And another thing,

468
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:13,240
it absorbs and dries quickly.

469
00:22:13,360 --> 00:22:15,000
A mould frame this big

470
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:17,960
absolutely has to be lightweight,

471
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:21,000
and the key is it can't warp.

472
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:23,240
I laid out three requirements,

473
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,920
and they agreed to all of them.

474
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:25,720
First,

475
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:28,480
it must be wild fir wood,

476
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,200
both hardness and toughness

477
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:30,680
have to be excellent.

478
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:31,880
Second,

479
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,960
the length must be 12 meters.

480
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:34,720
Third,

481
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:36,680
it must be naturally air-dried.

482
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,720
Kiln-dried won't do.

483
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,640
That's not easy to find.

484
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,280
Lao Kezi

485
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:46,520
called me on my way over just now.

486
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,400
He found it.

487
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,920
Wants me to come see it this afternoon.

488
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:49,720
That fast?

489
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:50,800
I know, right?

490
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,640
How can I not be thrilled?

491
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,480
Of course.

492
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,280
Yongnian,

493
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,200
look at how energetic you are.

494
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,320
Like you're 20 years younger.

495
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,560
Our Yongnian's about to do something big.

496
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:08,680
Almost 70 years old,

497
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,360
and 20 years younger, huh?

498
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:11,360
But still,

499
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,960
I'm confident.

500
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:15,640
I think the Three-Zhang-Three Xuan paper

501
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,320
just might be possible.

502
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,640
Fir wood 12 meters long,

503
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,840
same thickness at both ends, right?

504
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,080
Good, very good.

505
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,480
It's naturally grown, isn't it?

506
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,360
Get in touch about this one too.

507
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:26,480
Come take a look at this.

508
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:27,320
Have you contacted this one?

509
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,440
Why would I ask you for cultivated wood?

510
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:31,120
Cultivated wood isn't sturdy enough.

511
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,480
Old Xiao, Old Xiao, Old Xiao.

512
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,240
Air-dried, not kiln-dried.

513
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,320
Air-dried, kiln-dried won't do.

514
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:37,200
You hear me? Air-dried.

515
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,240
Hurry and find it for me, ask around.

516
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:38,440
Quick, quick.

517
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:40,000
Air-dried wood absorbs less water.

518
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:41,160
You got it?

519
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:42,920
Yes, yes, yes.

520
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:44,800
Aren't our requirements a bit too high?

521
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:45,160
Exactly.

522
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:45,320
Right.

523
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:46,360
High standards have their reasons.

524
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,720
This time, even if my Master

525
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,840
wanted Sun Wukong's Golden Cudgel,

526
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:49,680
I'd still have to find it for him.

527
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,200
That won't do.

528
00:24:15,560 --> 00:24:16,840
This one, this won't work, no good.

529
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:18,120
Swap it out, swap it out.

530
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,800
Oh right, I just remembered.

531
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:22,120
Which of us has a relative from Jiangxi?

532
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:23,480
Someone who deals in timber purchasing.

533
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:25,080
Pretty well-known around Jiangxi.

534
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:26,560
Who's from Jiangxi?

535
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:30,120
I heard Er Hu might have a relative there.

536
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:32,120
Right, it's Er Hu.

537
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,200
Er Hu.

538
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:35,440
Er Hu, hey Er Hu!

539
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:38,880
Look, this is all our family's timber.

540
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:39,680
Take a look.

541
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,040
It's still not quite right.

542
00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:42,840
Thank you, boss.

543
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,600
You're welcome.

544
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,600
Thank you, Director.

545
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,360
It's fine, it's fine, no problem.

546
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:49,120
Sorry for the trouble.

547
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:49,680
Come by anytime!

548
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,280
Alright, you get back to work.

549
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:51,160
No need to see me off, really.

550
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:51,800
Alright, goodbye.

551
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,840
How much longer till we get there?

552
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,640
About another hour.

553
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,440
My third uncle's factory

554
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,760
is famous all over Jiangxi.

555
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:13,280
They've got every kind of wood.

556
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:15,840
Take a break.

557
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:20,760
Go a bit faster.

558
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:24,360
Chief Xuan.

559
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,000
There's another workshop next door.

560
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:26,880
It's just a bit small.

561
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:27,880
How about we go take a look?

562
00:25:29,560 --> 00:25:30,360
Forget it.

563
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:33,760
These places all carry the same stuff.

564
00:25:34,120 --> 00:25:34,680
Chief Xuan.

565
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:38,200
Don't you think our standards are a bit too high?

566
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,360
Should we or not?

567
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,840
So, Brother Min, didn't I tell you?

568
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:00,440
Big enough, right?

569
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,320
We've got every kind of wood there is.

570
00:26:03,120 --> 00:26:03,440
All right.

571
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,240
Third Uncle.

572
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:17,960
So, how is it?

573
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,120
It's shade-dried,

574
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:21,040
but it isn't wild.

575
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:22,280
Boss,

576
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:23,560
don't play games with me now.

577
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:24,880
You want it 12 meters long.

578
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,760
Cultivated ones can grow tall enough,

579
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:29,280
but where would you find wild ones 12 meters long?

580
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,880
There's nothing I can do.

581
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:33,200
We insist on the wild ones.

582
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:35,120
All right then, go and look around.

583
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:35,920
If you find them,

584
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,120
I'll pay ten times the price.

585
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,560
Thank you, boss.

586
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:39,840
We'll look elsewhere.

587
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:43,720
Oh my goodness.

588
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,200
Chief Xuan.

589
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,040
We've asked everyone we could.

590
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,520
We've pulled every string too.

591
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:49,600
There really aren't any.

592
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,600
For a mould frame this big,

593
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,680
only wild wood will do.

594
00:26:58,120 --> 00:27:00,920
Cultivated wood lacks resilience,

595
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:03,560
and once it's lifted up,

596
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,840
it warps easily.

597
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:07,720
Besides, cultivated fir wood

598
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:09,240
absorbs way too much water.

599
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,840
How could the sheet-formers ever lift it?

600
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:13,600
We simply can't find any.

601
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:13,760
We really can't find any.

602
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,440
Can't find any...

603
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:17,520
We have to find it anyway.

604
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:15,440
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

605
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:16,880
Nine, ten.

606
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:18,320
That's enough.

607
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,120
Min.

608
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,080
Uncle, Uncle.

609
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,440
Come take a look at this, Uncle.

610
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,680
Come here and check it for me.

611
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:25,160
Tell me if this is wild fir wood.

612
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:25,840
All right, let me have a look.

613
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:26,360
Come on, come on.

614
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:26,840
It's fine, it's fine.

615
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,440
Easy now, easy.

616
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:27,880
Let me take a look.

617
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:28,880
Just those three pieces.

618
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:37,440
Yes.

619
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,320
Are you sure?

620
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,560
I'm sure.

621
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:42,040
This is wild fir wood.

622
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:58,360
Master.

623
00:28:59,320 --> 00:28:59,880
Take a look.

624
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:00,840
Master Xuan is here.

625
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,440
Old Xuan!

626
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:03,680
Come, come, come.

627
00:29:13,840 --> 00:29:15,680
Wild fir, naturally air-dried.

628
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,720
That's right, isn't it?

629
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,200
Take a look, take a look.

630
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:21,840
Now that's more like it.

631
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,440
Truly rare.

632
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,240
Absolutely.

633
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,840
This fir has some age to it.

634
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:31,520
Wild fir this precious, these days,

635
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:32,920
is extremely rare.

636
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,640
This apprentice of yours

637
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:35,840
really put his heart into it.

638
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:38,880
We even found fir this precious.

639
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,360
That's a good omen, I'd say.

640
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:43,200
How does that saying go again?

641
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,400
It's a long march ahead,

642
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:46,520
and this is the first step.

643
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:49,000
Master,

644
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:51,680
this credit

645
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,920
isn't mine alone.

646
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:54,080
We should thank Er Hu too.

647
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,440
Without him,

648
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:58,320
we'd never have found this lucky start.

649
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:02,160
That's right.

650
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:06,480
These two wild firs aren't cheap.

651
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,200
Xiao Min,

652
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:11,000
you can't pay for this out of your own pocket.

653
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,640
No, no, no, it's just pocket change.

654
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,360
I'll cover it.

655
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,440
Master Xuan,

656
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:17,160
You and President Xiao look after me so much.

657
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,920
These two logs are on me.

658
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,360
Your heart's in the right place,

659
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:22,760
but things should be done properly.

660
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,880
Let's do it by the rules.

661
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:26,560
All right.

662
00:30:26,560 --> 00:30:27,000
Lao Man,

663
00:30:27,320 --> 00:30:29,680
this money should come from us.

664
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:30,920
Say something.

665
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:31,920
Master Xuan,

666
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,840
if you approve of these two materials,

667
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:34,840
as for the money,

668
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,840
don't you worry about it.

669
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:37,240
You've got me, after all.

670
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:39,120
Fine, as long as he says it's proper.

671
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:39,560
Right.

672
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:40,640
Master,

673
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:41,600
if you're satisfied,

674
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,880
where should we deliver this wood?

675
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:43,880
Xiao Guo,

676
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,040
drive it straight back to the factory.

677
00:30:46,040 --> 00:30:48,160
Put it by the mould workshop door.

678
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:48,880
Got it.

679
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,320
Be careful.

680
00:30:58,560 --> 00:30:59,000
Let's go.

681
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,680
The length's enough.

682
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:01,480
More than enough.

683
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:02,400
Plenty.

684
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:03,720
Master Xuan,

685
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,920
now that the materials are chosen,

686
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:08,840
shouldn't we pick the people too?

687
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:12,760
The sheet-forming masters at Hongxing Factory

688
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,600
are all quite good.

689
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:16,800
They meet the requirements too.

690
00:31:17,320 --> 00:31:18,800
Now all that's left is

691
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,680
height and arm length.

692
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,920
These all need to meet the standard.

693
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:26,600
The key is finding the right leader.

694
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:27,960
That's crucial.

695
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:28,880
Master,

696
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,640
let me do it.

697
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,360
Master Xuan,

698
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,880
let me take part too.

699
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:35,680
We'll all sign up.

700
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,120
Lao Xuan,

701
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,000
I know

702
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,320
you want to find the Chief Papermaker.

703
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,720
Besides the Chief Papermaker,

704
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:46,960
drying and trimming

705
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:49,240
both need a leader too.

706
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:50,520
As for sheet forming,

707
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,240
Lao Man, you know it best.

708
00:31:52,320 --> 00:31:53,480
You speak up.

709
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,720
Each has his own strengths.

710
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:57,360
It's really hard to choose.

711
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:59,560
A Chief Papermaker over forty-odd men,

712
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:00,880
I've never had to pick one before.

713
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,560
You'd better take a look yourself.

714
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:03,920
Master Xuan,

715
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,520
how about we do this,

716
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,560
the way I see it,

717
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:07,840
everyone's here anyway.

718
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,200
Let all the qualified ones step up.

719
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:12,320
Let's go and pick them on the spot.

720
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,240
All right.

721
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:14,360
Let's go.

722
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:27,400
You don't have to stop what you're doing,

723
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:29,000
but hear me out for a moment.

724
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:31,640
Being able to make Three-Zhang-Three paper

725
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,680
is a truly glorious thing.

726
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:36,760
But if you can become the head Chief Papermaker,

727
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,440
that's the highest honor of all.

728
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:41,320
You all remember Master Xuan Yongnian, right?

729
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,880
The old Master Xuan

730
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,120
who used to work at our factory.

731
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,360
In a little while,

732
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:46,560
he'll be coming over here

733
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,520
to pick the head Chief Papermaker.

734
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:52,240
So show off your very best skills.

735
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,320
If any of you gets picked

736
00:32:54,320 --> 00:32:55,520
as the head Chief Papermaker,

737
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,680
I'll treat you to a meal and drinks.

738
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,000
Master Xuan.

739
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:03,200
Master Xuan.

740
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:08,320
Hard at work, Master?

741
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,040
Old Xuan.

742
00:33:59,960 --> 00:34:01,600
I've looked through all these workshops.

743
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:03,080
So many master craftsmen,

744
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,400
but not a single one

745
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,520
is fit to be a Chief Papermaker.

746
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,159
They're all seasoned masters,

747
00:34:15,159 --> 00:34:16,440
and their skills are good too.

748
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:17,880
But still,

749
00:34:18,679 --> 00:34:21,120
to lead the sheet-forming team,

750
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,679
none of them quite measure up.

751
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,960
With so many excellent masters here,

752
00:34:30,159 --> 00:34:31,800
you can tell just from a single glance?

753
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:35,520
No need to look. Use your ears.

754
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,320
Use... your ears?

755
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:40,639
A true expert doesn't need to look.

756
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:43,120
Just listen to the first scoop of water,

757
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:45,000
and everything becomes clear.

758
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:48,760
Is there really no one else?

759
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:51,320
Every qualified master is right here.

760
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:58,080
In the craft of papermaking,

761
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:01,680
only the sheet-forming master is a true artisan.

762
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:04,440
There's truth to that saying.

763
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:06,640
The shape of the paper

764
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:09,600
carries the personality of the sheet-forming master.

765
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:10,520
You know this.

766
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:15,080
Whether it's a drive for perfection,

767
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,680
or an untamed, defiant spirit.

768
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:19,320
In short, the sheet-forming master has character,

769
00:35:19,640 --> 00:35:21,160
and the paper he makes,

770
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,680
that's when it becomes living paper.

771
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:25,960
That reminds me of someone.

772
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:27,240
Who?

773
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:28,680
Wei Jianzhi.

774
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,200
Wei Jianzhi.

775
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,160
The single vat is off today, so he's not here.

776
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:37,120
Right, he works a single vat now.

777
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:43,200
No one will partner with him.

778
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,760
Anyone paired with him can't last three days.

779
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:48,280
The last master who partnered with him,

780
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,480
the two nearly got into a fight.

781
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:51,360
And why was that?

782
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:54,400
The man had made paper for twenty years,

783
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:56,760
yet Wei insisted he couldn't form sheets at all,

784
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:57,680
said he'd picked the wrong trade,

785
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,040
that he'd never truly learned the craft.

786
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,440
Let's go check out his workshop.

787
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:17,320
Old Xuan.

788
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:20,160
This is the vat where Master Wei forms his sheets.

789
00:36:37,560 --> 00:36:38,800
How long has Wei Jianzhi

790
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:39,920
worked at this vat?

791
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:43,720
Almost two years now.

792
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,600
He's the one.

793
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,520
Meet with him tomorrow and have a talk.

794
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:51,960
No, no, Master Xuan.

795
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:53,520
You... you haven't even met the man yet,

796
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,560
and you already think he'll do?

797
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:57,000
Nine times out of ten.

798
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,160
Take a look.

799
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:01,560
Look closely.

800
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:06,680
He's worn a tiny groove here.

801
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,160
Now look at the others'.

802
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:15,520
Theirs are flat, just a small patch.

803
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:17,040
What does that tell you?

804
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:20,360
It means his hands are steady.

805
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:24,680
Now look at where his feet stand.

806
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:32,160
He's worn marks where he always stands,

807
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:34,800
as if he's stood there for years.

808
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:35,520
Right.

809
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:39,160
It means his feet are steady.

810
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:41,000
Steady hands, steady feet,

811
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:44,000
that means his heart is steady too.

812
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:47,840
He's a meticulous man.

813
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:50,720
And a man like that

814
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:52,960
can turn out fine work.

815
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:55,360
So it's that simple?

816
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:59,640
Not simple at all.

817
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:03,240
First scoop hugs the body,

818
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:05,560
second scoop breaks the heart,

819
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:09,120
two hands set the thickness,

820
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:12,000
two feet reveal the spirit,

821
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,120
the mould lifts a thousand layers of snow,

822
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:17,520
the paper falls into eternal spring.

823
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,000
Look, so far

824
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,640
we've opened 34 stores.

825
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:27,400
Apart from a few like this one,

826
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:29,240
where we picked a poor location,

827
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:31,400
all the other 31 cultural stores

828
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,680
have all exceeded profit expectations.

829
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:34,800
That many?

830
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,520
Is that a lot?

831
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:38,480
Let me see.

832
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:39,480
Let me see.

833
00:38:40,120 --> 00:38:41,160
What are you looking at? You can't read it.

834
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:41,720
Let me see.

835
00:38:41,720 --> 00:38:42,160
Fine, fine, fine.

836
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:42,960
Stop drinking now.

837
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:43,400
You can't read it.

838
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:43,960
Let me see.

839
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:44,720
Fine, fine, fine.

840
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:49,640
Can you two stop staring at the money?

841
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:51,400
Can you show a little concern for me?

842
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:53,560
You're not allowed to drink any more.

843
00:38:54,720 --> 00:38:55,520
Master...

844
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:59,120
When Master picked the Chief Papermaker,

845
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,320
why didn't he choose me?

846
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:03,800
When your top disciple steps up,

847
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:05,720
I can breeze through it.

848
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,480
I can handle anything.

849
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:09,800
He didn't even consider my feelings,

850
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,400
he just stood up and left.

851
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:13,720
Stomped right off.

852
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,040
I was standing right here,

853
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:16,760
and he didn't even glance at me.

854
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:18,600
He just went and picked someone else.

855
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:20,160
If he'd at least looked at me once,

856
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:21,960
I'd feel a little better inside.

857
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,360
All right, all right, let me go check on him.

858
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,920
You two stay here and talk business.

859
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,000
Sure, sure, it's fine, it's fine.

860
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:29,760
He'll be fine once he throws up.

861
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:30,520
Sit, sit, sit.

862
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:33,240
He's always like this, it's fine.

863
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,200
Well, at any rate, right now,

864
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:38,040
our momentum is really strong.

865
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:40,360
Every store we open becomes a hit.

866
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:41,360
So I'm thinking,

867
00:39:41,520 --> 00:39:42,960
let's concentrate our cash flow,

868
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,960
and open 20 new stores right away.

869
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:45,960
We need to get on it fast.

870
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,200
You can't just

871
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,760
focus on the money.

872
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,320
Then what should we focus on?

873
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:52,280
You've got to focus on me.

874
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:54,280
We're a team, right?

875
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,000
We're all one team.

876
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,800
Aren't we?

877
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,640
We are.

878
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:01,440
Why do I have to patch up

879
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:04,840
that whole mess with my master?

880
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,160
Do you get it?

881
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:06,720
I get it, I get it.

882
00:40:06,720 --> 00:40:07,360
I'm not drinking.

883
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:08,960
Just have one sip.

884
00:40:11,760 --> 00:40:13,440
If you don't become the Chief Papermaker,

885
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,480
is your life over or something?

886
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:15,280
Wrong.

887
00:40:16,040 --> 00:40:18,320
I'm doing it to live a better life.

888
00:40:19,160 --> 00:40:20,680
When I left the Xuan family,

889
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:23,200
they cursed me for betraying my master.

890
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:25,040
Was I wrong?

891
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:28,080
I... I don't think I was wrong.

892
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:29,080
Brother Xiao Min,

893
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:31,800
you're not from Hongxing Factory, why pick you?

894
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,840
Good, very good.

895
00:40:34,720 --> 00:40:35,520
Well said.

896
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,560
Hurry, go on.

897
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:37,120
Fill it up.

898
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:38,040
Slow down, slow down.

899
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:39,000
What are you filling up so much for?

900
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:39,640
Fill the glass with wine.

901
00:40:39,640 --> 00:40:40,000
Fill it up.

902
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,400
Sit, sit, sit down, sit down.

903
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:43,720
But this time, the old man,

904
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:46,000
he's partnering with Hongxing Factory.

905
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:46,560
Right?

906
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:48,640
Hongxing Factory is full of talent.

907
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:50,240
Would it ever come around to you?

908
00:40:50,720 --> 00:40:50,960
No way.

909
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:53,040
If the old man forced you into that spot,

910
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,680
an apprentice who hasn't formed sheets in 20 years,

911
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:55,400
pushing you up there,

912
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,160
how would he explain that to Hongxing Factory?

913
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,360
No one would accept it.

914
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,120
You understand?

915
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:00,520
I understand.

916
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:02,720
If I were you,

917
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:03,840
right about now,

918
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:06,160
I'd stick close to the old man,

919
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:07,000
stay right by his side.

920
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:08,400
Do whatever I can do.

921
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:10,080
Odd jobs and chores,

922
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:12,000
boiling water, fetching his shoes.

923
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:13,080
Do whatever you can.

924
00:41:13,080 --> 00:41:14,240
Use your sincerity

925
00:41:14,680 --> 00:41:15,800
to move heaven and earth.

926
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,240
The old man will notice it.

927
00:41:57,040 --> 00:41:57,920
Is something wrong with you?

928
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,080
Yes.

929
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:01,440
What's wrong then?

930
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:04,280
Why can't you work with anyone?

931
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:08,480
I won't partner with people who have no integrity.

932
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:09,960
Watch your mouth!

933
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:10,920
Who has no integrity?

934
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:12,800
Not respecting your own craft

935
00:42:12,840 --> 00:42:14,800
is no different from trashing your own integrity.

936
00:42:18,040 --> 00:42:20,480
You're the Chief Papermaker for the team.

937
00:42:22,840 --> 00:42:23,640
But

938
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,840
if none of the sheet-forming crew respects you,

939
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:30,120
then I'll have to replace you.

940
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:35,400
Old Wei.

941
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,120
Get yourself well prepared.

942
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:47,760
Cao Deyong.

943
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:48,440
Here.

944
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:50,960
Joined the factory in 2004 to learn sheet forming.

945
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:52,400
Chief Papermaker for 16 years.

946
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:53,280
Zhang Qingliang.

947
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:53,680
Here.

948
00:42:54,120 --> 00:42:55,760
Joined the factory in 2001 to learn sheet forming.

949
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:57,120
Chief Papermaker for 18 years.

950
00:42:57,320 --> 00:42:58,000
Man Xiaochuan.

951
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:58,440
Here.
